metadata.name: 1st Order
metadata.description: Born of a faceless god, his origin unknown. His skin shimmers brighter than the Canopus star, eyes more mesmerising than Sirius. His tears, an elixir of youth, from his mouth flows the breath of life, the essence of existence he embodies. Existing at every angle, and without him, purpose and direction would never be known. He who has no name but is known by all.
